# Windsurf Rules for X-Twitter MCP

## X/Twitter Article Fetching

CRITICAL: Use `get_article` MCP tool for X/Twitter articles.
WebFetch and HTTP requests fail because articles need JavaScript rendering.

The `get_article` tool uses Playwright internally to properly render the content.

## When to Use get_article

Any URL matching:
- x.com/*/status/*
- twitter.com/*/status/*
- x.com/i/article/*

## Available Tools

Research: search_twitter, get_article, get_user_profile, get_tweet_details
Engage: favorite_tweet, retweet, bookmark_tweet
Publish: post_tweet, create_thread, quote_tweet
Social: follow_user, block_user, mute_user
